            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1679394053478-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> one-pot chicken breast & coconut pea-laf</strong> with the <strong>nigella yoghurt</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: Look out for the cardamom pod[s] and ginger pieces and discard them!</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
